000100**************************************************************            
000200*    ******                IMPORTANT                 ******  *            
000300*   TO INVOKE THIS PROGRAM FROM A CICS EXIT YOU MUST USE THIS*            
000400*   FORMAT:                                                  *            
000500*     CALL XL004-PGM     USING DFHEIBLK                      *            
000600*                              XL004-DEPT-COMMAREA           *            
000700*                              XL004-ITEM-COMMAREA           *            
000800*   IN BATCH DO THIS:                                        *            
000900*     CALL XL004-PGM     USING XL004-DEPT-COMMAREA           *            
001000*    ******                IMPORTANT                 ******  *            
001100*                                                            *            
001200*     INITIALIZE XL004-COMMAREA BEFORE CALLING XLKUT004      *            
001300*                                                            *            
001400*     XL004-DEPT-NBR IS REQUIRED                             *            
001500**************************************************************            
001600 01  XL004-DEPT-COMMAREA.                                                 
003400     05  XL004-KEYS.                                                      
003600         10  XL004-DEPT-NBR           PIC S9(04) COMP-3.                  
004100     05  XL004-RETURN-CODE            PIC X(02).                          
004200         88  XL004-SUCCESSFUL             VALUES ZERO.                    
004300         88  XL004-SQL-ERROR              VALUE '01'.                     
004300         88  XL004-NOT-FOUND              VALUE '13'.                     
004400         88  XL004-INVALID-INPUT          VALUE '99'.                     
004500     05  XL004-RETURN-SQLCODES.                                           
004600         10  XL004-SQLCODE            PIC S9(9).                          
005300     05  XL004-ERROR-PARAGRAPH-NBR    PIC X(5).                           
005400                                                                          
005500     05  XL004-OUTPUT-FIELDS.                                             
005600         10  XL004-DEPT-NM            PIC X(20).                          
005700         10  XL004-MDSE-LNE-CDE       PIC X(01).                          
005701         10  XL004-STR-ZN-CDE         PIC X(05).                          
005710         10  XL004-BUS-GP-NBR         PIC S9(03) COMP-3.                  
005711         10  XL004-BUS-GP-DESC        PIC X(25).                          
005730         10  XL004-BUS-AREA-ID        PIC S9(2) COMP-3.                   
005731         10  XL004-BUS-AREA-DESC      PIC X(25).                          
013200                                                                          
013300     05  FILLER                       PIC X(165).                         
013400     05  XL004-SQLCA                  PIC X(136).                         
013500 01  XL004-COMMAREA                   PIC X(01).                          
013600 01  XL004-PGM                        PIC X(08) VALUE 'XLKUT004'.         
